  <description>The photo shows Major Herman E. Smith, commandant of the Army Specialized Training Program Unit at the University of Chicago, with color guard, standing at attention on the quadrangles of the University campus at 11 a.m. yesterday (November 11) in observance of Armistice Day. All of the soldiers who are receiving special training at the University in the ASTP program participated in the observance at the flagpole on the quadrangles.</description>
